item.title: CVE-2018-5552|2024-08-05T05:40:50.601Z -- docutrac -- dtisqlinstaller.exe
item.description: Versions of DocuTrac QuicDoc and Office Therapy that ship with DTISQLInstaller.exe version 1.6.4.0 and prior contains a hard-coded cryptographic salt, "S@l+&pepper".

item.title: CVE-2018-5551|2024-08-05T05:40:50.612Z -- docutrac -- dtisqlinstaller.exe
item.description: Versions of DocuTrac QuicDoc and Office Therapy that ship with DTISQLInstaller.exe version 1.6.4.0 and prior contain three credentials with known passwords: QDMaster, OTMaster, and sa.
